# artemis1 example — generated artifact ignore list.
#
# Unlike the companion apollo11 example (which `.gitignore`s `*.png`
# and hosts visualization media via GitHub user-attachments), this
# example **commits the plot PNGs** because README.md references them
# directly (`![...](artemis1_*.png)`) and a committed copy makes the
# GitHub rendering work out-of-the-box without external hosting. The
# PNGs are small (< 320 KB each, ~1 MB total for the 4 files) and
# deterministically regenerable via `plot_trajectory.py`.

*.rrd
.cache/
.venv/
__pycache__/
